seo: 用友U8,OA,SQL注入漏洞,sqli,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测用友U8 OA系统是否存在test.jsp SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定的HTTP请求来验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the YongYou U8 OA system has a SQL injection vulnerability in test.jsp. It verifies the existence of the vulnerability by sending specific HTTP requests.
